### Update a cake
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/buscuits/69ade99149714da8019141ea
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 2.15
}

### Delete a cake
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/buscuits/69ade99149714da8019141ea